      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity analysis and uncertainty propagation must cover all influential input parameters.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but convergence was not demonstrated for all input parameters. Blood viscosity and hemolysis model coefficients remain incompletely characterized."
