      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sample-to-sample variability in experimental measurements must be quantified and reported.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark data used single-sample measurements at most operating points. Inter-sample variability was not characterized."
