    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile review, the seven assessed credibility factors all achieved required levels. The six unassessed factors are acknowledged as epistemic gaps but do not preclude acceptance at this review stage. The model provides sufficient evidence of credibility for the documented application based on available benchmark data and uncertainty quantification results.",
